A N A C T
RELATING TO INSURANCE -- CASUALTY INSURANCE RATING
***
1 This act would permit a motor vehicle liability insurance carrier to consider the zip code
2 of where a motor vehicle is garaged for purposes of calculating their policy premium so long as the
3 calculation of the zip code is segmented by the municipality where the vehicle is garaged. This act
4 would be effective upon policies issued on after July 1, 2026.
5 This act would take effect upon passage.
